     <p>Having trouble making a group decision?</p>
      Use this web app to poll your friends preferences.
      Create a poll with different options. Share the poll with your group and have them rank each option according to their preferences.
      We will calculate the results using the Borda Count Method so everyones opinions are incorporated in the final decision.
      <p>Learn more about the Borda Count Method <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borda_count">here</a>.</p>
